        rgo:text                "qui can. et preb. eccl. b. Marie ad Gradus Colon. 6 m. arg. via perm. <coram Theoderico [de Moers] aep. Colon.> c. Alexandro de Viseto Visero fam. <Juliani> [de Cesarinis] card. s. Angeli <legati in partibus Alamanie> pro alt. s. Johannis bapt. in eccl. s. Severini Colon. ac una vicar. de tribus [ad coll.] decani in eccl. ss. Appl. Colon. assec. est: de nova prov.; n.o. can. et preb. eccl. s. Cecilie Colon. et vicar. in eccl. Colon. insimul 10 m. arg., quos obtin. 27. ian. 34 S 292 259rs, 15. iul. 34 S 297 44vs, 29. aug. 34 exec.: decc. Veterisecclesie s. Pauli Monast., eccl. ss. Appl. ac eccl. s. Cuniberti Colon. exped. 2. oct. 34 L 324 204vss, de ref. 10. sept. 34 S 298 284rs, de ref. 15. sept. 34 S 302 137rs, l.b. oct. 34 T 4 36v, solv. 11 fl. pro compositione ann. p.m. cuiusdam Johannis s. palat. ap. aud. 16. mai. 1435 IE 397 31v, IE 398 30v." ;
        rgo:volume              "5" .

